John C Miller, chief executive 
officer of Denny's, says the company plans to expand franchise 
opportunities for its restaurants.  Miller talks to Bloomberg's 
 Kathleen Hays  on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 20:01
 